title: BBC - The Diary Of Anne Frank (2009)
description:
The Diary of Anne Frank is a BBC adaptation of The Diary of a Young Girl, written by Deborah Moggach. It was shown from January 5-9, 2009 in five half-hour episodes.



CAST

* Ellie Kendrick as Anne Frank
* Iain Glen as Otto Frank
* Tamsin Greig as Edith Frank
* Felicity Jones as Margot Frank
* Nicholas Farrell as Mr Dussel
* Kate Ashfield as Miep Gies
* Lesley Sharp as Mrs Van Daan
* Geoff Breton as Peter Van Daan
* Ron Cook as Hermann Van Daan
* Tim Dantay as Mr Kugler
